      Zumba

      • TV-PG
      • 237 Views

      Zumba is a high-energy fitness program inspired by Latin and international dance styles, combining cardio, muscle conditioning, balance, and flexibility into a lively and engaging workout. Created by Colombian dancer and choreographer Alberto "Beto" Pérez in the 1990s, Zumba has grown into a global phenomenon, loved by people of all ages and fitness levels.
